Patch Set 14:

This is mainly a bug fix patch rather than performance fix patch:

- support unaligned dio;
- lockless io data corruption; (lockless write will dirty client page cache without holding dlm lock, so before the dirty write back, different clients will see different data from same file?)
- fix bug like LU-3192;

Of course, it fixes the lockless io performance problem shown in b18801 at the same time.

Patch Set 14:

Sure, let's land the patch in that case. Can you please do two more things for me:
1. change the name of cl_io_lockless() to cl_io_cacheable();
2. get rid of CPT_TRANSIENT everywhere;
3. better to revise lloop device as well.
